import {Card} from "react-bootstrap";

const Bug = ({name,description}) => {
    console.log(name)
    console.log(description)
    return <Card style={{width: "18 rem"}}>
        <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>{name}</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{description}</Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
    </Card>
}

export default Bug
